Linera is the first real-time Layer-1 blockchain designed for the next generation of interactive, agentic applications.
Its core innovation is the microchain â€” a lightweight, parallel chain assigned to each user or app.
This architecture eliminates global bottlenecks, enabling instant finality, predictable scalability, and a Web3 experience that feels as fast as Web2.

